<RefNameDiv>
<RefName><command>satellite-sync</command></RefName>
<RefPurpose>
Incrementally synchronize an Red Hat Satellite's DB data and RPM repository with a parent Red Hat Satellite and pulling content from channel dumps.
</RefPurpose>
</RefNameDiv>

